** What Is @procoin Feeds? ** (my /firstdraft )

Here's how @bertwurst.eth described Feeds in a group chat: 

"Feeds is a new way to discover the best content on FC, curated by people you trust. Each feed focuses on a theme & when you find one you love, you can invest in it. That support helps the feed grow (in market cap), and in return, both curators and creators earn rewards. It's like subscribing to a playlist of top cast, where the community benefits together." 
(not that's one sharp dog going to one great puppy school!) üê∂  

It's a great use of your $PRO airdrop, and you get the coin of the feed. There's some tokenomics & a bonding curve to $PRO that I'll let @mjc716 explain for himself. Those of us who own a feed have invested to create our feed. ANYONE can create a feed for 50K $PRO. Most of the early creators invested 100K & some much more, betting on their own feed to do well. 

You've probably seen the Feeds mini app created by @mjc716 ... It hit #5  in pre-launch and remains a top-used mini app after Monday's release. Many trusted FCers have been sharing links, because many of us (including me) have our own Feed. 

